    "content" : "The transit between Los Angeles and the next destination took more or less 4 weeks. Before to start the all trip we knew that and we had to book the return ticket before to enter US. My dream was to visit Hawaii and Soizic's dream was to visit Japan. I was a little bit afraid to go to Japan because of the living cost. Hopefully we booked cheap flights tickets and we managed to visit both destinations. \n<br> We took off the 10th of October to Hawaii, Oahu and we found some couch surfing on a boat in Honolulu, cool ! We spent 1 week their and because it was the end of the end of our 3 months visa we left US to Japan. We spent 1 week in Tokyo and 1 week in Kyoto (in BnB). Off course, as VW enthusiasts, we went to Flat 4 Japan. \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/wink.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\";-)\" title=\"Wink\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/P1100437-360x480.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/P1100032-640x480.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/P1100330-640x480.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/P1100004-640x480.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> Honolulu, Hi, USA \n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1046-640x478.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1086-640x478.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_0845-640x478.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> Tokyo, Japan\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://www.leroadtrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1795-640x478.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> Nara, Japan\n<br> \n<br